ria-hidden="true"></i> University of Mannheim</li><li><a href="mailto:pooja.rani@uni-mannheim.de, rani@ifi.uzh.ch"><i class="fas fa-envelope" aria-hidden="true"></i> Email</a></li><li><a href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Pooja-Rani-2"><i class="fab fa-researchgate" aria-hidden="true"></i> ResearchGate</a></li><li><a href="https://twitter.com/poojaruhal"><i class="fab fa-twitter-square" aria-hidden="true"></i> Twitter</a></li><li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/pooja-rani-01985b68"><i class="fab fa-linkedin" aria-hidden="true"></i> LinkedIn</a></li><li><a href="https://github.com/poojaruhal"><i class="fab fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i> Github</a></li><li><a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=2B8GcJ4AAAAJ&hl=en"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Google Scholar</a></li><li><a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5127-4042"><i class="ai ai-orcid-square ai-fw"></i> ORCID</a></li></ul></div></div></div><article class="page" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/CreativeWork"><meta itemprop="headline" content="About me"><div class="page__inner-wrap"><header><h1 class="page__title" itemprop="headline">About me</h1></header><section class="page__content" itemprop="text"> <!--<p align="center"> <img src="http://localhost:4000/images/Pooja.JPG?raw=true" alt="Photo" style="width: 250px;"/></p>--><p>I am a Professor of Sustainable Software Engineering at the <a href="https://www.uni-mannheim.de/news/software-design-fuer-mehr-nachhaltigkeit/">University of Mannheim</a>, Germany where I lead the Sustainable Software Engineering Group. My research focuses on developing sustainable software systems and equipping developers with tools and methodologies to reduce environmental impact while improving the long-term quality, maintainability, and resilience of software systems.</p><p>Previously, I worked as an <a href="https://www.ifi.uzh.ch/en/seal/people/rani.html">Oberassistant/Senior Researcher</a> at <a href="https://www.uzh.ch/en.html">University of Zurich</a> with <a href="https://www.ifi.uzh.ch/en/seal/people/gall.html">Prof. Harald Gall</a>, <a href="https://www.ifi.uzh.ch/en/zest/people/pooja.html">Senior researcher</a> with <a href="https://sback.it/">Prof. Alberto Bacchelli</a>, and as a <a href="https://seg.inf.unibe.ch/team/">Postdoctoral researcher</a> with <a href="https://seg.inf.unibe.ch/people/timo/">Prof. Timo Kehrer</a>. I received my PhD (with honors) from the <a href="http://scg.unibe.ch/">Software Composition Group</a> at <a href="https://www.unibe.ch/">University of Bern</a> under the supervision of <a href="http://scg.unibe.ch/staff/oscar">Prof. Oscar Nierstrasz</a> and <a href="https://spanichella.github.io/">Dr. Sebastiano Panichella</a>. I also bring substantial industry experience in software engineering, having worked as a Software Engineer in testing in <a href="https://research.samsung.com/sri-n">Samsung</a>, as an Automation Engineer in <a href="https://www.vmware.com/">VMware</a>, and as a Software Developer in <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/atshaadidotcom/">People Interactive Ltd</a>. These experiences allow me to approach software engineering challenges from both academic and industrial perspectives.</p><h2 id="prospective-students-and-researchers">Prospective Students and Researchers</h2><p>If you are a motivated researcher, looking for a Master, PhD or Postodc position, checkout our <a href="https://www.wim.uni-mannheim.de/atkinson/team/prof-dr-pooja-rani/">Sustainable Software Engineering group</a> at the University of Mannheim. Please feel free to reach out to me before applying, to introduce yourself and describe your research interests. We currently have two open positions <a href="https://www.wim.uni-mannheim.de/atkinson/team/prof-dr-pooja-rani/join-us">PhD/Postdoc Positions</a>.</p><h2 id="recent-updates">Recent Updates</h2><ul><li>Recieved <a href="https://www.wuebben-stiftung-wissenschaft.org/en/news/better-software-and-technological-innovations">Wuebben Foundation</a> grant (~800k eur), 2025</li><li>Received a SNSF Project Grant (500k chf)-EdiSE (Energy-driven Integration in Software Engineering), 2025</li><li>Received the <strong>ACM SIGSOFT Distinguished Paper Award</strong> at ICPC, 2025</li><li>Gave a keynote at 7th International Conference on Information Systems and Management Science (ISMS-2024), NITK Kurukshetra, India, 2025</li><li>Received the <strong>Distinguished Reviewer Award</strong> at MSR, 2023</li><li>Received the <strong>Best PhD Thesis Award</strong> in computer science institutes of the University of Bern, Neuchatel, and Fribourg (JAACS) at Bern, Switzerland, 2022</li></ul></section><footer class="page__meta"></footer></div></article></div><div class="page__footer"><footer> <!-- start custom footer snippets --> <a href="/sitemap/">Sitemap</a> <!-- end custom footer snippets --><div class="page__footer-follow"><ul class="social-icons"><li><strong>Follow:</strong></li><li><a href="http://github.com/poojaruhal"><i class="fab fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i> GitHub</a></li><li><a href="https://poojaruhal.github.io/feed.xml"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-rss-square" aria-hidden="true"></i> Feed</a></li></ul></div><div class="page__footer-copyright">&copy; 2026 Pooja Rani. Powered by <a href="http://jekyllrb.com" rel="nofollow">Jekyll</a> &amp; <a href="https://github.com/academicpages/academicpages.github.io">AcademicPages</a>, a fork of <a href="https://mademistakes.com/work/minimal-mistakes-jekyll-theme/" rel="nofollow">Minimal Mistakes</a>.</div></footer></div><script src="https://poojaruhal.github.io/assets/js/main.min.js"></script> <script> (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){ (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o), m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m) })(window,document,'script','//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga'); ga('create', '', 'auto'); ga('send', 'pageview'); </script><